::Gigatron was in his new quarters, thinking about the war.  Would it ever 
come to an end?  Would the Keepers and Vulois be its downfall?  Or would 
Cybertrons be doomed to wage war forever.  A transformer can could live for 
millions of years, but they hardly achieve that great age.  Many die far too 
young or far too soon.  His thoughts then turned the two new bots, Feline and 
Skulletron.  He still didnt understand why they seemed so suspicious, but 
they did. He decides to take a rest, so he lies down and sleeps::
